data.description:
Stunning home nestled in the heart of Burleson Mansfield ISD on 1.6+ acres of expansive land. This gem offers a harmonious blend of space, style, and functionality.

Step into a beautifully remodeled kitchen, a culinary paradise featuring modern appliances, gleaming countertops, and ample storage. The heart of the home boasts an inviting brick fireplace, creating a warm ambiance for gatherings.

Newly updated flooring flows through the living spaces, marrying elegance and durability. The interior is bathed in natural light, courtesy of the newish windows, enhancing both charm and energy efficiency. 

Nature enthusiasts and equestrians will relish the opportunity to make the most of the vast land, perfect for horses and outdoor adventures.

With recent updates ensuring contemporary comfort, this property is more than a home; it's a lifestyle choice. Embrace tranquility. Sellers lender $5,000 temporary buy-down of the interest rate that will reduce the interest rate up to 1%.
